'''東部發展區'''（{{lang-ne|पुर्वाञ्चल विकास क्षेत्र|translit=Purwānchal Bikās Kshetra}}）是[[尼泊爾|尼泊爾]]的五個[[尼泊爾的發展區|發展區]]之一，又被稱為[[克拉底人|克拉底]]區。<ref>{{Cite book |title=Gorkhaland Movement: A Study in Ethnic Separatism |author=Amiya K. Samanta |publisher=APH Publishing |year=2000 |location=Darjeeling |pages=2,3}}</ref>東部發展區位於尼泊爾東部，面積 28456 平方公里，2011年時人口 5,811,555 人<ref name="Statoids" /><ref>{{Cite web |title=National Population and Housing Census 2011 (National Report) |author=Government of Nepal National Planning Commission Secretariat Central Bureau of Statistics |url=https://unstats.un.org/unsd/demographic/sources/census/2010_PHC/Nepal/Nepal-Census-2011-Vol1.pdf |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304110707/http://unstats.un.org/unsd/demographic/sources/census/2010_PHC/Nepal/Nepal-Census-2011-Vol1.pdf |location=Kathmandu, Nepal |date=2012-11 |access-date=2020-11-18 }}</ref>；首府設在[[丹庫塔|丹庫塔]]；丹庫塔同時也是[[丹庫塔區|丹庫塔區]]的政府所在地。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.myholidaynepal.com/places/eastern-development-region.html |title=Eastern Development Region |date= |website= |publisher=myholidaynepal.com |access-date=2018-02-14 |archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204203742/https://www.myholidaynepal.com/places/eastern-development-region.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.khullakitab.com/we-our-community-and-nation/notes/social-studies/class-10/162/practices |title= 1. Eastern Development Region |date=  |website=  |publisher= khullakitab.com |access-date= 2018-02-14 |archive-date= 2019-09-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190916140011/http://www.khullakitab.com/we-our-community-and-nation/notes/social-studies/class-10/162/practices |dead-url= no }}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
1961年4月13日，時任尼泊爾國王[[馬亨德拉|馬亨德拉]]將境內的35個區劃分為75個區，又設14個[[尼泊尔行政区划#專區（已于2015年废除）|專區]]下轄區級行政區；1972年，又在14個專區之上加設4個發展區，東部發展區是其中之一。<ref name="Statoids">{{cite web |url=http://cbs.gov.np/image/data/Population/Monograph_vol_1_2(1-10,11-21)/Chapter%252002%2520%2520Population%2520Size%2520Growth%2520and%2520Distribution.pdf |title=2.3 Spatial Distribution of Population |publisher=cbs.gov.np |access-date=2018-02-14 |archive-date=2018-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180902160201/http://cbs.gov.np/image/data/Population/Monograph_vol_1_2(1-10,11-21)/Chapter%2002%20%20Population%20Size%20Growth%20and%20Distribution.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年9月20日，在宣布新的《尼泊尔宪法 2015》时，所有發展區被廢除。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.statoids.com/unp.html |title=Provinces of Nepal |website=Statoids |access-date=2020-11-18 |archive-date=2017-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170718031612/http://www.statoids.com/unp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

